<bibRefCitation author="Evenhuis, N. L. &amp; Greathead, D. J." box="[763,1157,727,753]" pageId="67" pageNumber="68" refId="ref349891" refString="Evenhuis, N. L. &amp; Greathead, D. J. (1999) World catalog of bee flies (Diptera: Bombyliidae). Backhuys Publishers, Leiden, 756 pp." type="book" year="1999">Evenhuis &amp; Greathead (1999: 372)</bibRefCitation>
